OL,6,FThe scandal happened in the 1970s and
OL,7,F1980s, and after decades of
OL,8,Fcampaigning for justice, victims and
OL,9,Ftheir families are finally getting
OL,10,Fanswers in a milestone report.
OL,12,FWhat are the key findings from the
OL,13,Freport?
OL,15,FIn his damming report, Sir Brian said
OL,16,F"lives, dreams, friendships, families
OL,17,Fand finances were destroyed" by the
OL,18,Fscandal that "could have been
OL,19,Fprevented and should have been".
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G3/21
