OL,6,FHe places the majority of the blame
OL,7,Ffor the disaster on "successive
OL,8,Fgovernments," saying they showed
OL,9,F"little interest in finding the truth,
OL,10,Flistening to those infected, or taking
OL,11,Faction," and refused to admit
OL,12,Fresponsibility in order to "save face".
OL,14,FThere have been concerns from victims
OL,15,Fand campaigners for years there was a
OL,16,Fcover up by senior government and NHS
OL,17,Ffigures. The report compounds those
OL,18,Ffears by revealing key files "were
OL,19,Fdeliberately destroyed."
