OL,6,FThe files, which related to decision-
OL,7,Fmaking of the Advisory Committee on
OL,8,Fthe Virological Safety of Blood
OL,9,F(ACVSB), were marked for destruction
OL,10,Fin 1993.
OL,12,F"The destruction was not an accident,
OL,13,Fnor the result of flood, fire or
OL,14,Fvermin," Sir Brian wrote.
OL,16,F"The immediate reason for destruction
OL,17,Fwas human choice. Someone, for some
OL,18,Freason, had chosen to have those
OL,19,Fdocuments destroyed."
