OL,6,FThe report also reveals not only were
OL,7,Fpatients for HIV and Hepatitis C
OL,8,Ftested without their knowledge, they
OL,9,Fwere also not informed of the results
OL,10,Funtil in some cases years later,
OL,11,Fmeaning they carried the viruses for
OL,12,Fyears, infecting loved ones.
OL,14,FPeople were "denied the opportunity to
OL,15,Fcontrol the progression of their
OL,16,Fillness or to prevent its spread to
OL,17,Fthose close to them," Sir Brian writes.
