OL,6,FEighty haemophiliacs at Trelor's Boy's
OL,7,FSchool, in Hampshire, were given
OL,8,Finfected blood products as part of
OL,9,Ftheir treatment, and only 16 are still
OL,10,Falive today.
OL,12,FThere were 50 boys enrolled in a trial
OL,13,Fof a blood product made in the US,
OL,14,Fwhile neither they nor their parents
OL,15,Fwere informed they were part of the
OL,16,Ftrial.
