OL,6,FSome of the witnesses at the inquiry
OL,7,Fhave included senior politicians -
OL,8,Flike former prime minister Sir John
OL,9,FMajor, current Prime Minister Rishi
OL,10,FSunak, and former health secretaries
OL,11,FJeremy Hunt and Andy Burnham.
OL,13,FMultiple key documents in government
OL,14,Farchives are either missing or were
OL,15,Fdestroyed, which has led some
OL,16,Fcampaigners to suggest there was an
OL,17,Fattempt to cover up the scandal.
