OL,6,FThe inquiry's final report had been
OL,7,Fexpected in autumn last year, but the
OL,8,Fchair, Sir Brian Langstaff, said he
OL,9,Fneeded more time to prepare "a report
OL,10,Fof this gravity".
OL,12,FCabinet minister John Glen said on
OL,13,FMonday that he wishes the inquiry into
OL,14,Fthe scandal "had happened sooner", and
OL,15,Fthat "nobody has ever taken full
OL,16,Fresponsibility".
OL,18,FIt's expected the government will lay
OL,19,Fout their plans on how they will
OL,20,Fcompensate victims on Tuesday in
OL,21,FParliament.
